title: DAZ3D - Jason for Genesis Bundle - (DAZ 13747) - Installer (Gene
description:
Jason is a carefully crafted toon guy for Genesis, created in a typical 3D Universe style. Combining features from several of 3D Universe's other cartoon guys, Jason brings the typical western cartoon guy style to the Genesis platform.

Utilizing the power of the Genesis platform enables Jason to be mixed with any other Genesis figure. Combine him with Hiro, The Freak, Michael 4, or any other Genesis figure to create your own totally unique character.

Add stylish and fun clothing Jason. Designed to compliment Jason perfectly, these clothing items can be combined for various looks, from casual to formal. Use the included extra textures to create your own unique outfits.
